    <item>
      <title>Jolidon：降息 50 个基点反映数据疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/jolidon-50-basis-point-cut-reflects-weaker-data-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，现在是美联储下调关键政策利率的时候了。瑞银瑞士及全球股票联席主管 Eleanor Taylor Jolidon 与 Joumanna Bercetche 就中东和非洲展望进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/jolidon-50-basis-point-cut-reflects-weaker-data-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:24:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列与黎巴嫩紧张局势加剧冲突风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/israel-lebanon-tensions-raise-risk-of-wider-conflict-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[100 架以色列战机袭击黎巴嫩南部数小时后，周一紧张局势有所缓和，但局势仍然严峻，爆发地区性战争的风险仍然存在。控制风险副总监 Niamh McBurney 与 Joumanna Bercetche 就中东和非洲地平线进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-26/israel-lebanon-tensions-raise-risk-of-wider-conflict-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
